About this area

Paradise Island

Located in Paradise Island, The Reef at Atlantis is next to a golf course and on a private beach. Fort Montagu and Nassau Public Library are local landmarks, and the area's natural beauty can be seen at The Retreat Garden National Park and Lucayan Archipelago. Travelling with kids? Consider Aquaventure, or check out an event or a game at Haynes Oval. With scuba diving, parasailing and surfing/body boarding nearby, you'll find plenty of adventures in the water.

About this property

The Reef at Atlantis

4.5-star luxury resort by the ocean
18 holes of golf, a casino and a marina are just a few of the amenities provided at The Reef at Atlantis. This resort is a great place to bask in the sun with a private beach, a beach bar and beach massages. Treat yourself to a body wrap, a facial or a deep-tissue massage at the on-site spa. The on-site coffee shop, Starbucks, features light fare. The gym offers aerobics classes and yoga classes; other things to do include volleyball, snorkelling and basketball. Free in-room WiFi is available to all guests, along with free water park access and a nightclub.
Other perks include:
  • An outdoor pool and a children's pool, with a lazy river, a waterslide and cabanas
  • Limo/town car service, buffet breakfast (surcharge) and 6 outdoor tennis courts
  • Valet parking (surcharge), express check-out and supervised childcare (surcharge)
  • Concierge services, a porter/bellboy and golf clubs on-site
  • Guest reviews give top marks for the pool
Room features
All 497 rooms have comforts such as air conditioning and dressing gowns, as well as perks such as free WiFi and safes.
Extra conveniences in all rooms include:
  • Childcare services and free infant beds
  • Bathrooms with separate baths/showers and free toiletries
  • HDTVs with premium channels and DVD players
  • Balconies or patios, wardrobes/cupboards and kitchens

    • Deposit: USD 250.00 per accommodation, per day

    • Fee for buffet breakfast: from approximately USD 30 to 50 per person
    • Airport shuttle fee: USD 35 per person (return)

    • Valet parking fee: USD 20 per day

    The above list may not be comprehensive. Fees and deposits may not include tax and are subject to change.

    Please note that cultural norms and guest policies may differ by country and by property; the policies listed are provided by the property

    We should mention
